# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# ─── AI PROVIDER KEYS (Multi-model foundation) ───────────────────────
# Add each key in BOTH places:
#   1. Supabase Edge Functions  → supabase.com/dashboard → your project
#      → Edge Functions → Manage secrets → add secret
#   2. Cloudflare Workers       → wrangler secret put <NAME>
#      (or Cloudflare Dashboard → Workers → Settings → Variables → Secrets)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ─── REQUIRED NOW (Phase 1) ──────────────────────────────────────────

# Anthropic (already in use — primary model)
# Get from: console.anthropic.com → API Keys
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=""

# Cloudflare AI Gateway (already in use — routes Anthropic traffic)
# Get from: Cloudflare Dashboard → AI → AI Gateway → your gateway
CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID=""
CLOUDFLARE_AI_GATEWAY_ID=""
# Build the URL as: https://gateway.ai.cloudflare.com/v1/{ACCOUNT_ID}/{GATEWAY_ID}
CLOUDFLARE_AI_GATEWAY_URL=""

# ─── PHASE 2: Add when ready to enable multi-provider routing ────────

# OpenAI — hot standby fallback for all Claude routes
# Get from: platform.openai.com → API keys → Create new secret key
OPENAI_API_KEY=""

# Grok (xAI) — real-time market data for competitor-scanner, gtm-strategy-builder
# Get from: console.x.ai → API Keys (requires xAI account)
GROK_API_KEY=""

# DeepSeek — cost-optimised batch tools (seo-audit, kpi-dashboard, email-sequence)
